  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚠ <strong>Early supporter price $4.99 — increases to $9.99 on March 27.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/1a82ab05578c093de4ad5d318efcc4b2.webp?t=1773927458\" width=585 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics-based trampoline game focused on dynamic ragdoll movement</strong>, advanced trick systems, and full mid-air control. Perform tricks and build high-scoring sequences across 35+ unique arenas with distinct physics rules and environmental conditions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/4cb7f9ce0391d9c19a9871a2a190df37.poster.avif?t=1773927458\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/4cb7f9ce0391d9c19a9871a2a190df37.webm?t=1773927458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/4cb7f9ce0391d9c19a9871a2a190df37.mp4?t=1773927458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arenas include backyard trampolines, professional gym setups, circus layouts, multi-trampoline parks, and low-gravity environments. Each setting introduces distinct layouts and trampoline configurations that materially affect movement and scoring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/563d32eaf58f53aae3e044d164ef12e7.poster.avif?t=1773927458\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/563d32eaf58f53aae3e044d164ef12e7.webm?t=1773927458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/563d32eaf58f53aae3e044d164ef12e7.mp4?t=1773927458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/15b14baa72e361a8a12098a9a248c741.webp?t=1773927458\" width=585 height=62 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Active animated ragdoll system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full mid-air body control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advanced trick combo system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35+ unique arenas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distinct arena physics and trampoline configurations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alternative game modes and skill challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable tricks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple athletes with unique movement attributes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full support for all gamepads & Steam Deck</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/768a138cd7532282c544f77d607af357.poster.avif?t=1773927458\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/768a138cd7532282c544f77d607af357.webm?t=1773927458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/768a138cd7532282c544f77d607af357.mp4?t=1773927458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚠ <strong>Early supporter price $4.99 — increases to $9.99 on March 27.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/1a82ab05578c093de4ad5d318efcc4b2.webp?t=1773927458\" width=585 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics-based trampoline game focused on dynamic ragdoll movement</strong>, advanced trick systems, and full mid-air control. Perform tricks and build high-scoring sequences across 35+ unique arenas with distinct physics rules and environmental conditions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/4cb7f9ce0391d9c19a9871a2a190df37.poster.avif?t=1773927458\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/4cb7f9ce0391d9c19a9871a2a190df37.webm?t=1773927458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/4cb7f9ce0391d9c19a9871a2a190df37.mp4?t=1773927458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arenas include backyard trampolines, professional gym setups, circus layouts, multi-trampoline parks, and low-gravity environments. Each setting introduces distinct layouts and trampoline configurations that materially affect movement and scoring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793770/extras/563d32eaf58f53aae3e044d164ef12e7.poster.avif?t=1773927458\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/